                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                    <div id="about" class="tabcontent">
                        <h1 class="font-weight-bold mb-4">Best Family-Friendly Hotels in India for a Perfect Getaway | Book My Hotels</h1>

                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm mb-4">
                            <p>
                                India is a land of diverse cultures, stunning landscapes, and warm hospitality — making it one of the best destinations for family vacations. Whether it’s a relaxing beach holiday, a mountain escape, or a royal experience, India offers countless options for families to bond and create lifelong memories.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                At <strong>Book My Hotels</strong>, we’ve curated a list of the best family-friendly hotels in India, perfect for every budget and travel style.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 1 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">1. The Leela Palace – Udaipur</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    If you’re looking for luxury, The Leela Palace Udaipur offers a truly royal experience. Overlooking Lake Pichola, it’s one of the best family resorts in Rajasthan, combining heritage architecture with modern comfort.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Families can enjoy boat rides, Rajasthani cultural evenings, and spacious suites with lake views — perfect for kids and parents alike.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 2 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">2. Novotel Goa Resort & Spa – Goa</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    When it comes to family-friendly beach hotels in India, Novotel Goa tops the list. The resort has family suites, a kids’ play area, swimming pools, and easy access to Candolim Beach.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Parents can relax at the spa while kids enjoy fun activities at the supervised play zone. Plus, the hotel serves a variety of cuisines — including Indian dishes that suit every palate.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 3 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">3. Club Mahindra Kanatal – Uttarakhand</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Nestled in the hills near Mussoorie, Club Mahindra Kanatal offers an unforgettable mountain experience. Perfect for adventure-loving families, the resort features zip-lining, bonfires, and nature walks.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    The cozy cottages and panoramic Himalayan views make it one of the best hill station resorts for families in North India.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 4 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">4. Taj Green Cove Resort & Spa – Kovalam, Kerala</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    For families looking for a serene coastal escape, Taj Green Cove in Kovalam is a gem. Spread over lush greenery and backwaters, it combines traditional Kerala architecture with five-star comfort.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Kids can enjoy the pool and beach activities while parents unwind at the world-class Jiva Spa. The resort’s warm hospitality ensures a memorable family holiday in South India.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Hotel 5 -->
                        <div class="card mb-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">5. The Tamara Coorg – Karnataka</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    For nature lovers, The Tamara Coorg is an eco-friendly resort offering coffee plantation tours, nature trails, and musical evenings.
                                </p>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Families can relax in luxurious cottages amidst misty hills. With its perfect mix of comfort and sustainability, it’s among the top family-friendly resorts in South India.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Why Choose -->
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm mt-5">
                            <h4 class="mb-3">Why Choose Book My Hotels?</h4>
                            <p>
                                At Book My Hotels, we understand what Indian families truly value — comfort, safety, and affordability. Our platform helps you find verified hotels, compare family packages, and enjoy exclusive discounts across India.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Whether you’re planning a summer vacation, weekend getaway, or festive trip, we make hotel booking simple, secure, and budget-friendly.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                So, pack your bags and get ready to explore the best family-friendly hotels in India. From royal palaces to beach resorts, mountain retreats to heritage stays — Book My Hotels brings your dream family vacation just a click away!
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
